clinical_study.brief_title: Post-Marketing Surveillance of Prazaxa速 on the Long-term Use in Patients With Nonvalvular Atrial Fibrillation
clinical_study.official_title: Post-Marketing Surveillance on the Long-Term Use of Prazaxa速 Capsules in Patients With Nonvalvular Atrial Fibrillation

brief_summary.textblock: To investigate the safety and efficacy of long-term use of Prazaxa速 Capsules in patients with nonvalvular atrial fibrillation for preventing the occurrence of ischemic stroke or systemic embolism (SEE).

primary_outcome.measure: Frequency (Percentage) of Participants With Adverse Drug Reactions
primary_outcome.time_frame: Up to 104 weeks from first administration of study drug
primary_outcome.description: Percentage of participants with adverse drug reactions (ADRs) is presented. An ADR is defined as an adverse event (AE) for which either the investigator or the sponsor (or both) assess the causal relationship to Prazaxa速 Capsules either as "Related", "Probably related", or "Cannot be denied".

secondary_outcome.measure: Incidences of Stroke and Systemic Embolism (SEE)
secondary_outcome.time_frame: Up to 104 weeks from first administration of study drug
secondary_outcome.description: Incidence rate of Stroke and SEE (number of patients per 100 patient year) with 95% confidence interval (CI) is reported. Stroke and SEE were recorded as adverse events (AEs) of special interest. Exact Poisson confidence intervals are presented for incidence rate.

criteria.textblock:
Inclusion criteria:
- Patients with nonvalvular atrial fibrillation who have never received Prazaxa Capsules for preventing the occurrence of ischemic stroke and systemic embolism will be included.
Exclusion criteria:
- None

participant_flow.recruitment_details: Post-Marketing Surveillance on the Long-Term Use of Prazaxa速 Capsules in patients with nonvalvular atrial fibrillation
participant_flow.pre_assignment_details: 6772 subjects were enrolled. Among them, Electronic Case Report Form (eCRF) was not collected for 144 subjects and 185 subjects were excluded because of them not following registration rule, no actual visit or previous treatment experience with Prazaxa, leaving 6443 subjects eligible for study who were enrolled and included in the final study.

group.title: Patients With NVAF
group.description: Patients with nonvalvular atrial fibrillation (NVAF) taking daily oral dose of Prazaxa速 Capsules (Dabigatran etexilate). Dosage of Dabigatran etexilate approved in Japan: 300 milligram (mg) daily (150 mg [as 2 capsules of 75 mg] twice a day (b.i.d)) or 220 mg (110 mg [as 1 capsule of 110 mg] b.i.d)

clinical_results.limitations_and_caveats: The study was conducted in an unblinded manner and without controls. The explanatory power of the study results was limited and the study results should be interpreted with the necessary caution.
